  "label": "Simeon Drahl",
  "description": "This individual is a middle-aged human of brown skinTone, with brown eyes set beneath pronounced brow ridges that give the face a permanently appraising cast. Black hair is kept in a plain, close-cropped cut that exposes a high hairline and a broad, squared forehead. The nose is blunt and slightly flattened, and the mouth is wide with a persistent asymmetry at the left corner. The hands are large and densely callused, with old, cleanly healed knife nicks across the knuckles that record long service behind a bar.",
